		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Size Guide</h2>		
			<h4>Women / Shirts</h4>		
		<p>VASIA own buy sizes are designed to fit the following body measurements. Some brands may vary from these measurements but you can still use them as a guide.</p>		
